Package edu.smcm.ai.sliding_block

This package contains all of the classes implementing the Sliding Block Puzzle environment for use in the algorithms in edu.smcm.ai.search.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ManhattanDistance
    A heuristic that computes the sum of the Manhattan distances between the tiles and their correct positions.
    OutOfPlace
    A heuristic that simply counts the number of tiles that are not in their correct place in the puzzle.
    SlidingBlockAction
    Actions in the Sliding Block Puzzle.
    SlidingBlockProblem
    Implementation of the abstract Problem class for the Sliding Block Puzzle.
    SlidingBlockState
    Sliding Block Puzzle State.
    SlidingBlockState.Coordinate
    Coordinate of a tile in the puzzle.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    SlidingBlockAction.ActionType
    The enumeration of the possible actions.
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    ImplementationException
    An exception that is thrown when there is an error in the implementation.

Package edu.smcm.ai.sliding_block Description

This package contains all of the classes implementing the Sliding Block Puzzle environment for use in the algorithms in edu.smcm.ai.search. See Russell and Norvig, Artificial Intelligence: A Modern Approach, Third Edition, p.70-71.
